Die!

800
01:01:15,088 --> 01:01:17,006
You deserve to die!

801
01:01:17,840 --> 01:01:21,094
Why did my daughter have to die?
You should die!

802
01:01:21,177 --> 01:01:23,763
You're the one who deserves to die!

803
