01:01:39,779 --> 01:01:41,739
-Goodness!
-Goodness, ma'am!

809
01:01:53,501 --> 01:01:54,794
Sang-tae.

810
01:02:00,633 --> 01:02:01,718
Just me…

811
01:02:03,511 --> 01:02:07,140
Just direct your hate only towards me.

812
01:02:13,813 --> 01:02:15,481
I'll take all of it.

813
01:02:17,400 --> 01:02:20,653
